%N A015726 Inverse of 1717th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015726 Periodic with period length 1717. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015726 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015726/b015726.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015726 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1717.
%H A015726 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1600">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1600.
%H A015726 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015726 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
%t A015726 CoefficientList[Series[1/Cyclotomic[1717,x],{x,0,110}],x] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Dec 30 2019 *)
%o A015726 (PARI) first(n)=Vec(1/polcyclo(1717)+O(x^(n+1))) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Jun 01 2026
